{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/database/mysql/mysql-cheat-seat/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"あさくちブログ"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ec0b54e0-5187-5381-97a0-39119c0f80d0","excerpt":"Docker でさくっとデータベースを用意する MYSQLROOTPASSWORD は必須。 MySQL 接続 -u user_name -ppassword -P port_num -h host_name -D db_name host_name…","html":"<h1>Docker でさくっとデータベースを用意する</h1>\n<p>MYSQL<em>ROOT</em>PASSWORD は必須。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">docker run -d <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    -p <span class=\"token number\">3306</span>:3306 <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --name mysql-container-name <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    -v mysql-volume-name:/var/lib/mysql <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    -e <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>password <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    mysql:8.0.26</code></pre></div>\n<h1>MySQL 接続</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mysql -u root -p</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>-u user_name</li>\n<li>-p[password]</li>\n<li>-P port_num</li>\n<li>-h host_name</li>\n<li>-D db_name</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>host_name について</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">-h localhost</code>（もしくは<code class=\"language-text\">-h</code>なし）で接続するときは、あらかじめ <code class=\"language-text\">~/.my.cnf</code> に以下の設定が必要。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">[client]\nprotocol=TCP</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">-h 127.0.0.1</code> なら 👆 の設定は不要。</p>\n<h2>password について</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>—password[=password], -p[password]</p>\n<p>If given, there must be no space between —password= or -p and the password following it.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>パスワードを渡すときはスペースを開けずに渡す。\nなんでこんな仕様？？？？</p>\n<h1>データベース一覧</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"mysql\"><pre class=\"language-mysql\"><code class=\"language-mysql\">mysql&gt; show databases;</code></pre></div>\n<h1>データベース接続</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"mysql\"><pre class=\"language-mysql\"><code class=\"language-mysql\">mysql&gt; use mysql</code></pre></div>\n<h1>テーブル一覧</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"mysql\"><pre class=\"language-mysql\"><code class=\"language-mysql\">mysql&gt; show tables;</code></pre></div>\n<h1>テーブル定義</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"mysql\"><pre class=\"language-mysql\"><code class=\"language-mysql\">mysql&gt; desc func;</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"MySQL チートシート","date":"August 14, 2021","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/database/postgresql/postgresql-cheat-seat/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"PostgreSQL チートシート"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"ec0b54e0-5187-5381-97a0-39119c0f80d0","previousPostId":"d44f588b-779f-5abc-8a05-cb0d35c95154","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3348849317"]}